title: The Blue streak rocket
creator_credit: George Grafton Green and Rank Organisation Film Productions
brief_description: The Blue Streak Rocket is the first stage in the development of a rocket which will help boost a one ton satellite, of the European Launcher Development Organisation, into orbit three hundred miles high. Shows the static test in England and the launching at Woomera.
